      "instruction": "<p>Bash the <strong>lemongrass</strong> with a <strong>rolling pin</strong></p><p>Remove the<strong> tough outer layer<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> and set aside for later</p><p>Chop the <strong>softer inner core<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> finely</p><p>Peel and chop the <strong>brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>into wedges</p><p>Chop the <strong>waxy potatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Trim, then chop the <strong>green beans</strong> in half</p>",
