            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>onion wedges </strong>with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>Once beginning to soften, add the <strong>halved waxy potatoes </strong>and cook for 2 min further or until the potatoes are coated in spices</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
