    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>in 325ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your<strong> coconut stock</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>coconut stock </strong>and <strong>tamarind paste </strong>to the pan and cook, covered, for 13-15 min or until the potatoes are almost fork-tender</p>",
