    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the potatoes are cooking, deseed the<strong> pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p><p>Crush the <strong>roasted peanuts</strong> with a <strong>rolling pin</strong></p>",
