    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are almost fork-tender, discard the <strong>cardamom pods</strong> from the curry</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced pepper </strong>and<strong> chopped green beans </strong>and cook, covered, for 4-5 min further or until the veg is cooked through<strong> </strong>–<strong> </strong>this is your <strong>massaman-style vegetable curry</strong></p>",
