      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>massaman-style vegetable curry </strong>over the <strong>lemongrass rice</strong></p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into small bowls and turn out!</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>crushed roasted peanuts</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
